## Ground Truth (Revealed After Exercises)

> **Do not read this before completing both exercises.**

<details>
<summary>Reveal ground-truth parameters</summary>

| Channel | True ROI | Adstock Decay | Saturation Shape |
|---|---|---|---|
| TV | 2.1x | 0.80 (slow decay) | Strongly saturating |
| Paid Search | 4.3x | 0.35 (fast decay) | Mild saturation |
| Social | 2.8x | 0.50 (medium decay) | Moderate saturation |
| Display | 1.4x | 0.40 (fast decay) | Strongly saturating |

Baseline (non-media) accounts for ~55% of revenue. Holiday weeks add ~18% lift. Price index has a -0.6 elasticity.

</details>

